short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Click cancel on the Lesson Complete popup on LaraCasts.com.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This simple extension listens for the lesson complete popup on the LaraCasts.com website while watching lesson videos. When the popup appears, the extension clicks the cancel button.

This extension is fully free and opensource. There is no warranty or guarantee. No data is collected by this extension.

https://github.com/syntaxseed/laracasts-no-autoplay
